{"_path":"/travel/singapore_zone1","_dir":"travel","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_empty":false,"title":"新加坡濱海灣花園及金沙酒店","description":"這一天除了參觀濱海灣花園的花穹、雲霧林及超級樹，以及金沙酒店的觀景台和夜景。","id":"2023s4","draft":false,"image":{"src":"/assets/img/travel/sg/roofview2.JPG","alt":"金沙酒店觀景台"},"head":[{"name":"og:title","content":"新加坡濱海灣花園及金沙酒店 | IngridKao travel"}],"modified":"2023-04-06","tags":["2023新加坡自由行","景點安排"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這一區主要觀賞花穹-雲霧林-超級樹-金沙酒店，時間安排一整天會比較充裕，雖然在地圖上感覺會走到脫水，但三個景點的步行範圍大致上只有一個大安森林公園的大小，雖然當地溫度很高但花穹和雲霧林室內都有適合人的控溫，甚至在花穹裡室內溫度僅18度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建議早上先去『濱海灣花園』，接近下午三點左右到『濱海灣金沙空中花園觀景臺』的門票兌換卷先抽號碼牌，再到金沙酒店的商場走走等候入場時間。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-vertical"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofTicket1.JPG",":alt":"'門票兌換卷先抽號碼牌'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"極推薦使用Klook的\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"links","props":{"href":"https://tinyurl.com/2a2y7fjs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"花穹+雲霧林(阿凡達：全新體驗)+金沙空中花園觀景臺套票"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n，這個套票在一月的時候購買價格約台幣1,635元，使用QRcode就可以通行(如果擔心網路連線也可以印製出來使用)；這次發現新加坡很會做生意，和日本像糖果無害包裝的方法不同，新加坡則是全部一次列給你看你想怎麼組合搭配，如果沒有事先買好套票在現場買會貴非常多，並且會耗費很多時間排隊購買門票。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-horizontal"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofview1.JPG",":alt":"'金沙空中花園觀景臺'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"交通方式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"交通方式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坐地鐵到"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海灣舫"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，地鐵上方為金沙酒店，一出地鐵閘口往右是濱海灣花園和天空樹，往左是商場(包含Apple store及雨眼、舢板船-室內貢多拉、賭場)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"濱海灣公園garden-by-the-bay"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"濱海灣公園Garden by the bay"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不知道為什麼新加坡的景點很難拍的很美，後來覺得可能是人工感太重，很難拍出有味道的照片，現場看真的蠻壯觀的所以會有很大的驚喜感！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建議將這一區的行程排在白天，加上正中午真的不適合在室外移動，且*花穹（Flower Dome）、雲霧林（Cloud Forest）*兩個景點有陽光照射會漂亮很多，以下是行程安排："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海灣舫閘口出來，往"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Garden by the bay*的標示走會看到一個長長的地下連通道，走上地面會走到戶外售票亭，如果當天下雨或是想省體力可以在售票亭購買接駁車票卷，僅販售來回車票價個新幣3元，可以搭乘到花穹、雲霧林會場，不過由於回程直接走到天空樹supertree沒有使用回程接駁車。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接駁車會到花穹及雲霧林會場，如果有列印klook票卷，『花穹』及『雲霧林』這兩個地方都可以讓工作人員掃QR code入場不用特別換票。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"個人較建議先看『花穹』，相對『雲霧林』裡面普通很多(我只在裡面待半小時左右)，出口會接到紀念品購買區域，出來馬上可以接到雲霧林入口。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"到2023年6月前『雲霧林』有阿凡達特展，不得不說原本雲霧林就很壯觀，但再加上阿凡達的元素真的會讓人回到電影場景。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-vertical"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/CloudForest2.JPG",":alt":"'雲霧林阿凡達特展'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{"start":5},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雲霧林出口會引導到剛剛的紀念品購物區，外面有點心販售區賣飲料咖啡冰淇淋等西瓜口味很好吃，稍作休息後前往天空樹supertree；不過路途上會經過shake shake和starbucks，也可已選擇在這兩處用餐。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步行約十分鐘會抵達"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"天空樹(supertree)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，之前看照片的時候以為更加龐大所以不覺得壯觀，這次因為是一個人來所以卯起來健行(行軍)，分了兩個時段來看不同時段的天空樹，白天和晚上的感覺不一樣，比較推薦晚上來到這邊。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-vertical"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/CloudForest1.JPG",":alt":"'雲霧林門口'"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  \t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/CloudForest3.JPG",":alt":"'雲霧林阿凡達特展'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"金沙空中花園觀景臺skypark"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"金沙空中花園觀景臺skypark"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出發前可以再確認一次夕陽時間，出發前查詢日落時間是19:20，預計前半小時抵達就可以看到整個日落晚霞。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"確認觀景臺時間\n看完白天的supertree可以經由空橋往skypark前進，空中花園觀景臺"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"位置在金沙酒店三棟（最北邊）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，跟著指標一出門口會看到很多遊客排隊，給飯店工作人員看QRcode後會發一張『時段號碼牌』，依據指定時間前往入口。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"這次實際使用在17:00拿到七點的號碼牌，提早半小時前約18:30抵達入口時工作人員開放進入；不過這樣會讓後面燈光秀的時間很倉促，建議還是早一點取號碼牌。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中間等待時間\n可以趁這段時間逛逛商品區域，就算不想購物也可以去下列地點去去："},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"links","props":{"href":"https://nedkahn.com"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ned kahn的作品"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"links","props":{"href":"https://nedkahn.com/portfolio/rain-oculus"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雨眼Rain Oculus"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："},{"type":"text","value":"每兩個小時運轉一次，實際時間需要看現場公告；由於這個水柱讓下方"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"舢板船"}]},{"type":"text","value":"有動力可以前進。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"links","props":{"href":"https://nedkahn.com/portfolio/wind-arbor"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wind Arbor"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："},{"type":"text","value":"這個是晚上從天空樹準備去坐地鐵，下樓前往後一看突然發現牆壁像水波一樣在動覺得非常美，回家查才發現是同一人的作品"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全球首間水上Apple Store：從商場手扶梯進入建築球體很像進入萬神殿，這棟建築很神奇的不是用挖掘的方式建造，而是用埋管的方式將地下連通道放在海灣下；後來才看書才知道新加坡除了是金融、海運中樞，更是東南亞地區地底纜線最密集的國家，因此在海底建置方面的技術非常先進。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-vertical"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/appleStore.JPG",":alt":"'水上Apple Store'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"- 海灣景色\n- 賭場（個人沒去）\n","meta":null},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"- 海灣景色\n- 賭場（個人沒去）\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. skypark觀景臺\n返回skypark入口給工作人員確認票卷和時間等候卡，手扶梯往下後會看到售票及檢查點，帶著klook票卷和時段預約卡再次檢查入場。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"電梯一下子會到52樓，往西北是海灣東南是濱海灣公園，如果在七點時段可能有機會看到夕陽，雖然這次天候不佳但也同時看到白天和夜晚的景色。\n","meta":null},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"電梯一下子會到52樓，往西北是海灣東南是濱海灣公園，如果在七點時段可能有機會看到夕陽，雖然這次天候不佳但也同時看到白天和夜晚的景色。\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-horizontal"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofTicket2.JPG",":alt":"'正式的門票'"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofview1.JPG",":alt":"'七點的天色景觀'"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofview2.JPG",":alt":"'觀景台往東看'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"濱海灣及天空樹的燈光秀"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"濱海灣及天空樹的燈光秀"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"金沙燈光秀20:00、21:00(週五週六有增加22:00)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"天空樹燈光秀19:45、20:45"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["img-vertical"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\t"},{"type":"element","tag":"images","props":{":path":"/img/travel/sg/roofview4.jpeg",":alt":"'夜晚的天空樹'"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果想要"},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同一天觀賞到濱海灣及天空樹的燈光秀"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，建議從skypark下來後先去濱海灣20:00的燈光秀。濱海灣的最佳觀賞角度在一樓外平台，從skypark到一樓平臺路程約15分鐘。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"金沙燈光秀\n燈光秀沒有煙火，所以如果不是超大雨感覺不會停止舉辦，整個表演約15分鐘；不過因為僅水柱和雷射光，個人覺得香港那種搭配建築物的燈光秀較為壯觀。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"燈光秀參考"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{"start":2},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"天空樹燈光秀"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以看第二場20:45，這樣行程會比較順；這邊如果下雷雨就可能會停止，畢竟這些大樹可能是個巨大避雷針。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果時間沒有這麼多或是攜家帶口帶眷不好移動，要在濱海灣和天空樹燈光秀之中選一個的話，我會選擇去看天空樹。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關文章"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關文章"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/travel/singapore_preparation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"入境及進入市區交通"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/travel/singapore_hotel"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新加坡住宿-牛車水及克拉碼頭"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/travel/singapore_spot"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新加坡景點安排及紀錄"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/travel/singapore_food"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"食紀"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":true},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"footnote-label","className":["sr-only"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"target":"_blank","rel":["noreferrer","noopenner"],"className":["text-xs"],"href":"https://mimihan.tw/sands-water-dance/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"【參考文章】Mimi韓 - 濱海灣金沙酒店水舞秀：演出時間＆交通彙整，新加坡必看絢麗夜間燈光秀"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"交通方式","depth":2,"text":"交通方式"},{"id":"濱海灣公園garden-by-the-bay","depth":2,"text":"濱海灣公園Garden by the bay"},{"id":"金沙空中花園觀景臺skypark","depth":2,"text":"金沙空中花園觀景臺skypark"},{"id":"濱海灣及天空樹的燈光秀","depth":2,"text":"濱海灣及天空樹的燈光秀","children":[{"id":"相關文章","depth":3,"text":"相關文章"}]},{"id":"footnote-label","depth":2,"text":"Footnotes"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:travel:5.singapore_zone1.md","_source":"content","_file":"travel/5.singapore_zone1.md","_extension":"md"}